{"word":"ἰσόμοιρος","slug":"ἰσόμοιρος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἰσόμοιρος</b></el> <el>(ἰσό-μοιρος, ον) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:μοῖρα'><el>μοῖρα</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>sharing equally</i> or <i>alike</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>coextensive</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>; <el>γῆς ἰσόμοιρ' ἀήρ</el> earth's <i>equal partner</i> air, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}